act.article:
2 Definitions.—In these rules, unless the context otherwise requires,—
a “Act” means the Depositories Act, 1996 (22 of 1996);
b “adjudicating officer” means the officer appointed by the Board as adjudicating officer under section 19H of the Act;
c “inquiry” means the inquiry referred in section 19H.
2 Words and expressions used herein and not defined in these rules but defined in the Depositories Act, 1996 shall have the same meanings respectively assigned to them under that Act.
